title: Darkest Dungeon Build 7701
description:
Build Update #7701 (PC and Mac)

    More improvements to save file handling
    Hero barks are now rendered in front of UI elements
    Fixed game breaking issue that allowed you to dismiss to lower than 4 heroes when a hero was on extended leave in stress recovery (bender, vision quest, etc.) - it no longer counts that missing hero as one of the remaining four
